          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="timeline-panel border rounded shadow-sm h-100 p-4">
          <h4 class="text-uppercase text-primary small">Users</h4>
          <p class="small text-muted mb-0">
            Authenticated identities can reach profile workflows and uploads where your rules allow it.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="timeline-panel border rounded shadow-sm h-100 p-4 border-danger-subtle bg-danger-subtle">
          <h4 class="text-uppercase small text-danger-emphasis">Administrators</h4>
          <p class="small text-muted mb-0">
            Higher privilege for CRUD changes and guarded surfaces such as generated admin scaffolding.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
